title: Petition/Application Was Rejected For Insufficient Funds
body: On April 12, 2021, we rejected your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190128698 because your filing fee was returned by your financial institution for insufficient funds. Any previously assigned priority or processing date is no longer applicable. If you wish to still pursue the benefit, you must file a new application or petition and submit a new fee filing fee. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
